  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uF9DW3Q.png\" alt=\"Title\" /></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/mars_\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/ko--fi-donate-FF5E5B?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=ko-fi&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on ko-fi\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jeb_-wool\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1081749?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/jeb_-wool\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/jeb_-wool?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a> </strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />This mod adds jeb_ Wool, which can be obtained by shearing a sheep named jeb_. With this wool, you can craft a new jeb_ Banner, Carpet, and Bed. These blocks function like their Vannila counterparts.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jRiQqlP.gif\" width=\"484\" height=\"270\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p></center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://mars-the-planet.github.io/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/a1a13adf-7c67-48f1-8d6e-e08334434df1.png\" /></a></p>",
